      "root_cause": "src/db/index.ts calls mongoose.connect(baseUri) at module-load time, before db-connect.ts beforeAll can connect to the worker-specific database. Pipeline test imported @/db, triggering early connection to base URI. db-connect.ts then saw readyState=2 and waited for that connection (to base DB), leaving both workers on the same default database. Additionally, createAdminUser() used getMongoClient().db() which resolved to a different database than mongoose.connection.",
